<h3 id="3-berlin---colchester-bcmi">3. berlin - colchester BCMI</h3>
<p>This project experiments with sending BCMI data via the internet using <a href="https://tunnelblick.net/">Tunnelblick</a> between two countries. The method developed by Fredrik is primarily tested to understand how the Interface could be used for real-time BCMI performances online.</p>
